# ground.obj — a large flat ground plane (400 x 400 units, centered at origin,
# lying on y = 0). Give it a Model component and tint it (e.g. green) to act as
# the ground under the world. Each face is listed with both windings so the
# surface shows whether viewed from above or below.
o Ground

v -200.0 0.0 -200.0   # 1
v  200.0 0.0 -200.0   # 2
v  200.0 0.0  200.0   # 3
v -200.0 0.0  200.0   # 4

f 1 2 3
f 1 3 4
f 1 3 2
f 1 4 3
